name: Tangle Breaker
summary: Tangle Breaker is a fun and engaging puzzle game that challenges you to untangle colorful ropes! Each level gets more difficult as the knots grow more complex, testing your problem-solving skills and strategic thinking. With its vibrant 3D graphics and intuitive controls, it's suitable for all ages. Twist, pull, and unravel the ropes to solve the puzzles. Are you ready to become the ultimate Tangle Breaker? Jump in and enjoy hours of addictive fun!
